703728f-a.text:
Columbia Street, east side, south from and across Baltic Street. The garage and four-story building, this side of Baltic Street, are
on the N. E. corner.
View 2 shows the N. E. corner buildings, the garage extending
also on Baltic Street(right).
October 15, 1940
Views 1,2
P. L. Sperr
